headline: The Club Is Yours With EA SPORTS FC™ 26: Jude Bellingham and Jamal Musiala Revealed as Cover Stars of EA SPORTS FC’S Most Community-Driven Title
summary: REDWOOD CITY, Calif., July 16, 2025--Today, Electronic Arts Inc. (NASDAQ: EA) announced generational talents Jude Bellingham and Jamal Musiala as the cover athletes for EA SPORTS FC™ 26 and EA SPORTS FC Mobile, while also revealing a first-look at EA SPORTS FC 26 gameplay, ahead of its worldwide launch on September 26, 2025.

headline: Zum Appoints JoAnn Covington as General Counsel
summary: Zūm, the leader in modern student transportation, today announced the appointment of JoAnn Covington, who joins the company as General Counsel. Covington will work with the Zum management team and Board to provide strategic legal advice and set governance policies as Zum continues to deliver safe, reliable, sustainable and equitable student transportation nationwide.
